title: BRIEF-Nickel One Resources Announces Private Placement Of $500,000 And Closes $336,000 First Tranche
text: March 19, 2018 / 11:18 PM / in 11 minutes BRIEF-Nickel One Resources Announces Private Placement Of $500,000 And Closes $336,000 First Tranche Reuters Staff March 19 (Reuters) - Nickel One Resources Inc: * NICKEL ONE RESOURCES INC. ANNOUNCES PRIVATE PLACEMENT OF $500,000 AND CLOSES $336,000 FIRST TRANCHE * NICKEL ONE RESOURCES INC - ‍ARRANGED NON-BROKERED PRIVATE PLACEMENT OF UP TO 10 MILLION UNITS AT $0.05/UNIT TO RAISE AGGREGATE PROCEEDS OF UP TO $500,000​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
